                  Kanapathippillai Cumanan and
                  Xuchu Dai},
	title = {Performance Analysis for the GSVD-Based {MIMO-NOMA} Communications
                  via Operator-Valued Free Probability},
	journal = {{IEEE} Trans. Wirel. Commun.},
